---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/CtaBand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Services | Canyon Strategic Wealth"
  description="Coordinated wealth management for Utah families and business owners — investment management, financial planning, tax strategy, estate planning, risk management, and business owner advisory."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Our Services</h1>
    <p>Comprehensive, coordinated wealth management — every piece of your financial life working together.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="vfo-section">
      <div>
        <div class="section-eyebrow dark">The Virtual Family Office</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">One Team. Every<br />Aspect of Your<br />Financial Life.</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Traditional advisors manage investments. We coordinate your entire financial ecosystem — acting as the strategic quarterback across every discipline.</p>
        <p class="section-subtitle">This means your investment strategy, tax planning, estate plan, and risk management aren't siloed — they're integrated into one cohesive strategy that evolves with your life.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vfo-hub">
        <svg class="vfo-lines" viewBox="0 0 400 400">
          <line x1="200" y1="200" x2="200" y2="40" />
          <line x1="200" y1="200" x2="360" y2="120" />
          <line x1="200" y1="200" x2="360" y2="260" />
          <line x1="200" y1="200" x2="200" y2="360" />
          <line x1="200" y1="200" x2="40" y2="260" />
          <line x1="200" y1="200" x2="40" y2="120" />
        </svg>
        <div class="vfo-center">Your<br />Strategy</div>
        <div class="vfo-spoke">Investments</div>
        <div class="vfo-spoke">Tax Planning</div>
        <div class="vfo-spoke">Cash Flow</div>
        <div class="vfo-spoke">Estate Planning</div>
        <div class="vfo-spoke">Risk Mgmt</div>
        <div class="vfo-spoke">Business Advisory</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--gray);">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div class="section-eyebrow dark">What We Manage</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Services Built Around Your Life</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="services-detail-grid">
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-in">
        <div class="sdc-icon sky"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" /><path d="M14.5 9.5c-.5-1-1.5-1.5-2.5-1.5-1.66 0-3 1-3 2.5S10.34 13 12 13c1.66 0 3 1 3 2.5S13.66 18 12 18c-1 0-2-.5-2.5-1.5" /><path d="M12 6v2" /><path d="M12 16v2" /></svg></div>
        <h3>Investment Management</h3>
        <p>Strategic portfolio construction aligned with your goals, risk tolerance, and time horizon. We continuously monitor and rebalance to keep you on track.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Goal-aligned portfolio construction</li>
          <li>Ongoing monitoring and rebalancing</li>
          <li>Tax-efficient management</li>
          <li>Regular performance reporting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-in">
        <div class="sdc-icon sky"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h2" /><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1" ry="1" /><line x1="8" y1="10" x2="16" y2="10" /><line x1="8" y1="14" x2="16" y2="14" /><line x1="8" y1="18" x2="16" y2="18" /></svg></div>
        <h3>Comprehensive Financial Planning</h3>
        <p>A holistic plan that covers every dimension of your financial life — retirement projections, cash flow analysis, education funding, and wealth preservation.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Retirement income projections</li>
          <li>Cash flow optimization</li>
          <li>Education funding strategies</li>
          <li>Net worth tracking and analysis</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-in">
        <div class="sdc-icon gold"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10" /><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4" /><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14" /></svg></div>
        <h3>Tax Strategy &amp; Coordination</h3>
        <p>We coordinate directly with your CPA to implement proactive tax strategies — not just at year-end, but throughout the year.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Roth conversion analysis</li>
          <li>Tax-loss harvesting</li>
          <li>Charitable giving strategies</li>
          <li>Year-round CPA coordination</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-in">
        <div class="sdc-icon gold"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22" /></svg></div>
        <h3>Estate Planning Coordination</h3>
        <p>We work with your estate attorney to ensure your legacy is protected, your documents are current, and your beneficiary designations are aligned.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Will and trust coordination</li>
          <li>Beneficiary designation review</li>
          <li>Legacy and wealth transfer planning</li>
          <li>Power of attorney guidance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-in">
        <div class="sdc-icon sky"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" /></svg></div>
        <h3>Risk Management &amp; Insurance</h3>
        <p>A comprehensive review of your insurance coverage to identify gaps and protect against risks across your life, family, and business.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Life and disability insurance review</li>
          <li>Long-term care planning</li>
          <li>Property and liability coverage</li>
          <li>Umbrella policy assessment</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-in">
        <div class="sdc-icon gold"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="2" width="16" height="20" rx="1" /><line x1="9" y1="6" x2="9" y2="6.01" /><line x1="15" y1="6" x2="15" y2="6.01" /><line x1="9" y1="10" x2="9" y2="10.01" /><line x1="15" y1="10" x2="15" y2="10.01" /><line x1="9" y1="14" x2="9" y2="14.01" /><line x1="15" y1="14" x2="15" y2="14.01" /><path d="M10 22v-4h4v4" /></svg></div>
        <h3>Business Owner Advisory</h3>
        <p>For business owners, we look at your enterprise as part of your overall wealth strategy — maximizing value today while planning for tomorrow.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Business valuation integration</li>
          <li>Succession and exit planning</li>
          <li>Retirement plan design</li>
          <li>Executive compensation strategies</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    heading="Let's Build Your Strategy"
    text="Every great financial plan starts with a conversation."
    ctaLabel="Schedule Your Discovery Call"
  />
</BaseLayout>
